	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Anes wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">does spr dma takes 512 or 513 cpu cc?<br /><br />if it needs 1 cycle to read and 1 cycle to write it would seem 512, but i have heard about 513.</div>
<br />It takes 513. The extra cycle is apparently to wait for the CPU to finish the instruction properly before the DMA controller grabs the bus. These extra cycles are also why sample playback DMA takes four cycles instead of one.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


